all\" id=\"wb-srch-sub\" name=\"wb-srch-sub\" type=\"submit\"><span class=\"glyphicon-search glyphicon\"></span><span class=\"wb-inv\">Search</span></button>\n</div>\n</form>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<nav class=\"gcweb-menu\" typeof=\"SiteNavigationElement\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Menu</h2>\n<button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Main </span>Menu <span class=\"expicon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-offset-6 col-xs-6 col-md-offset-0 col-md-4\">\n<section id=\"wb-so\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Sign in</h2>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/account.html\"><span class=\"visible-xs\">IRCC sign in</span><span class=\"hidden-xs\">IRCC sign in</span></a>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada.html\">Live in Canada</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/provincial-nominees.html\">Immigrate as a provincial nominee</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/provincial-nominees/express-entry.html\">Provincial Nominee Program : Express Entry process</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<nav class=\"provisional gc-subway\">\n<h1 id=\"gc-document-nav\">Provincial Nominee Program: Express Entry process</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/provincial-nominees/express-entry/eligibility.html\">Who can apply</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/provincial-nominees/express-entry/eligibility.html#gc-document-nav\">Who can apply</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/provincial-nominees/express-entry/get-confirm-nomination.html\">Get or confirm a nomination</a> <a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/provincial-nominees/express-entry/get-confirm-nomination.html#gc-document-nav\">Get or confirm a nomination</a></li>\n<li><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"active\" href=\"#\">Apply for permanent residence</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<h1 class=\"gc-thickline\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Apply for permanent residence</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>If we invite you to apply for permanent residence, you’ll get a message in your account that includes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>which program you’re invited to apply for</li>\n<li>the next steps you should take</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you’re invited, <strong>you have 60 calendar days to apply for permanent residence online</strong>.</p>\n<h2>1. Check the program requirements</h2>\n<p> Make sure you’re <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/eligibility.html\">eligible for the program</a> you’re invited to apply for.</p>\n<p>By checking the program’s eligibility requirements you‘ll be</p>\n<ul>\n<li>more prepared to apply</li>\n<li>able to decide if you should accept the invitation to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>If your personal situation has changed</h3>\n<p>If your situation (or that of your spouse or partner) has changed, you should <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/immigrate/skilled/crs-tool.asp\">recalculate your score</a> before applying for permanent residence online.</p>\n<p>If your new score is less than the <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/submit-profile/rounds-invitations.html\">lowest score allowed in your round of invitations</a>, you should decline the invitation. If you decide to apply anyway, we may</p>\n<ul>\n<li>refuse your application</li>\n<li>not refund your application fee</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Some examples of changes that could lower your score include</p>\n<ul>\n<li>you no longer have a <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/documents/offer-employment.html\">valid job offer</a></li>\n<li>you no longer have a provincial nomination</li>\n<li>your language test scores\n  <ul>\n<li>have expired</li>\n<li>are lower after you retested</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2. Apply for permanent residence</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>Follow our instructions to <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/apply-permanent-residence.html\">apply for permanent residence through Express Entry</a>.</p>\n<p>You’ll need to pay</p>\n<ul>\n<li>the processing fee</li>\n<li>biometric fees</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You must apply within 60 calendar days. If you <strong>don’t apply within that time</strong> (and you don’t decline the invitation)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>the invitation will expire and</li>\n<li>we’ll remove your profile from the pool</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If we remove you from the pool, to be considered in future rounds of invitations, you’ll have to</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fill out and submit a new Express Entry profile</li>\n<li>meet the eligibility requirements</li>\n<li>be accepted into the pool again</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li>\n<details>\n<summary><h3>If you decline an invitation to apply</h3></summary>\n<p>If you decline an invitation, we’ll put you back into the Express Entry pool of candidates. We’ll consider your profile in future rounds of invitations <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/eligibility.html\">if you’re still eligible</a>.</p>\n<p>The cut-off score varies from round to round. If your score isn’t high enough, we might not invite you to apply again. In some cases, to be invited to apply again you may need to</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/submit-profile/waiting-pool.html#improve\">improve your score</a></li>\n<li>update your Express Entry profile</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There’s no guarantee we’ll invite you to apply again.</p>\n<p>Declining an invitation <strong>won’t affect</strong> whether or not we invite you to apply again later (when we put you back into the pool).</p>\n</details>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"wb-disable-allow\" data-ajax-replace=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/feedback/page-feedback-en.html\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-02-19\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-fo